                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4333" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0611</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9126 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长袖善舞，多钱善贾:新准则视角下雅戈尔财技大揭秘</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From the perspective of new accounting standards reveal Youngor financial technology</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张劲松，于珊，隋宝玉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨商业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雅戈尔</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">可供出售金融资产；长期股权投资；转换；金融资产减值损失</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Available for sale of financial assets, long-term equity investment, conversion, loss of impairment of financial assets</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018年1月底，雅戈尔突然对中信股份的投资计提33亿元减值准备，造成公司净利润暴跌9成。两个月后，4月10日，又将上述投资从可供出售金融资产调整为长期股权投资，并依据净资产核算，造成公司净利润暴增近7倍，而扣除非经常性损益后的净利润，恰恰与账面净利润相反。雅戈尔对金融资产的会计处理带给我们太多的思考。本案例对雅戈尔扭亏为盈进行了深度剖析，探讨了新准则下金融资产重分类对企业盈余管理的影响，分析了雅戈尔对金融资产重分类的灵活运用，金融资产重分类对财务报表的影响，研究了雅戈尔盈余管理的手段。案例研究表明，新准则下金融资产重分类及其核算方法的变更对企业财务报表产生重要影响，为企业盈余管理方法和手段提供了新的视角。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At the end of January 2018, Youngor suddenly set aside 3.3 billion yuan for the investment of Citic Limited, resulting in a 90% plunge in the company&#39;s net profit. Two months later, on April 10, the above-mentioned investment was adjusted from the financial assets available for sale to long-term equity investment, and according to the accounting of net assets, the net profit of the company increased by nearly 7 times, and the net profit after deducting non-recurring profit and loss was exactly the opposite of the book net profit. Youngor&#39;s accounting treatment of financial assets brings us too much thinking. This case makes an in-depth analysis of Youngor&#39;s conversion from loss to profit, discusses the impact of financial asset reclassification on enterprise earnings management under the new criteria, analyzes Youngor&#39;s flexible application of financial asset reclassification, the impact of financial asset reclassification on financial statements, and studies Youngor&#39;s earnings management methods. The case study shows that the reclassification of financial assets and the change of accounting methods under the new standards have an important impact on the financial statements of enterprises, which provides a new perspective for the methods and means of earnings management of enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">盈余管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
